Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:43.90,Main,Outlined line,0,0,0,,{\fad(250, 0)\blur2\bord5\3c&HF6FBF6&}I envy you, Tenjou-senpai... \N getting to live with such a feminine girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:44.74,Main,Outlined line,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord5\3c&HF6FBF6&}Is that sarcasm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.42,Main,Outlined line,0,0,0,,{\fad(250, 0)\blur2\bord5\3c&HF6FBF6&}Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:01.90,Main,Outlined line,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord5\3c&HF6FBF6&}Himemiya! You have to \N play the piano for Mickey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:05.14,Main,Outlined line,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord5\3c&HF6FBF6&}He seems really fixated \N on your playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.14,0:23:07.13,Main,Outlined line,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord5\3c&HF6FBF6&}If you insist, Utena-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:08.82,Main,Outlined line,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord5\3c&HF6FBF6&}No, don’t do it because I say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:09.95,Main,Outlined line,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord5\3c&HF6FBF6&}Do it for Mickey’s sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:11.29,Main,Outlined line,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord5\3c&HF6FBF6&}I am the Rose Bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:13.75,Main,Outlined line,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord5\3c&HF6FBF6&}I will do whatever \N my fiancé requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:19.25,Main,Outlined line,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord5\3c&HF6FBF6&}Wake up, Mickey! This isn’t the way \N to get Himemiya to play for you!
