Comment: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:29.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{Prologue}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:40.43,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,In the end, it still \N came down to this, Mickey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:44.58,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Yes. I have to recapture that music.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:48.47,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,And so, I need the Bride \N no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:52.93,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Sitting at a piano \N suits you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:54.68,Main,Juri,0,0,0,,I quite agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:02:00.85,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I will make the Rose Bride mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:03.85,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Even if it means hurting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:41.63,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,You play the piano \N so wonderfully, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:43.39,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,You’re the pride of the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:47.90,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Your performance at the party really made \N all of the flower arrangements shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:51.40,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,But why did you decline \N entering the competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:54.40,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,The teachers were so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:02.58,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,This piano seems to be \N slightly off key.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:06.21,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Really? It was tuned \N just last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:14.22,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Then maybe I’m the one \N in need of tuning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:23.22,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,You always play this piece \N when you’re alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.98,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, \N I only play because of this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:32.60,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I keep playing in hopes \N a certain someone will hear this music.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:34.44,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,“A certain someone”?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.98,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,But I can’t play it \N quite the way I’d like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:41.20,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,No matter what, \N I can’t get the sound I seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:44.41,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Far from it! \N Sounds just fine to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.93,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,It broadcasts your feelings \N loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:54.46,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,You can’t play this piece, not unless you \N possess eternal beauty within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:57.72,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,And what’s the song’s name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:00.14,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,“The Sunlit Garden”.
Comment: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:00.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:17.03,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,Aw, crap... \N This is the worst grade I’ve ever gotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:19.53,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Hmm... That’s a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:24.41,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,Honestly, I think I know all the math I’ll ever need \N with just the basic multiplication tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:27.85,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Pretty sure it’s to cultivate \N our ability to think logically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.53,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,But as my mom \N always told me:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:33.77,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,“A truly fine woman foists all of \N the logical thinking onto men.”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.03,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:38.80,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,I’m sure you did well \N since you’re good at math.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:41.90,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:45.27,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,You’re not usually \N this bad at math, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:47.08,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,I was a little distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:50.89,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,That’s no good. Gotta keep \N cultivating that logical reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:51.45,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:55.46,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Anyway, I can’t act bubbly \N after getting a grade like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:57.40,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.79,Main,Aiko,0,0,0,,You {\i1}do{\i0} know \N how much we love Mickey, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:20.37,Main,Keiko,0,0,0,,We heard all about it! Because of you, \N our Mickey said no to entering the competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.84,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,I... I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:27.35,Main,Aiko,0,0,0,,Liar. You had to have said something \N that made him lose his confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:28.64,Main,Keiko,0,0,0,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.85,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,I never said anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:39.57,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,You there! \N What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:49.66,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Seems like you were wrongfully \N blamed about something on my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.62,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I’m truly sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.00,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:56.83,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,It’s nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:05.66,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:07.06,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:10.14,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Who’s that boy with Himemiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.56,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,Oh, that’s Mickey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:14.43,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,“Mickey”?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:17.92,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,Don’t you know about him? \N He’s Kaoru Miki-kun, a middle school first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:21.79,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,Not only is he a pretty boy \N who’s nationally ranked at piano and fencing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:26.72,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,he’s also a genius taking college classes \N even though he’s only a first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:28.04,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:31.70,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,Plus, he’s really popular \N with older girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.69,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,Mitsuko and her friends \N never stop talking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:36.54,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:41.80,Main,Wakaba,0,0,0,,Why’s he with Himemiya Anthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.35,Main,Juri,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:58.13,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Juri-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:01.67,Main,Juri,0,0,0,,I thought I’d find you \N in the club room or the Council office,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.40,Main,Juri,0,0,0,,but here you are \N studying in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.48,Main,Juri,0,0,0,,Are you correcting \N someone’s test?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:07.91,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Yes, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:09.20,Main,Juri,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:12.97,Main,Juri,0,0,0,,That’s a change. \N You usually keep your distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:15.37,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Say, Juri-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:19.78,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Happiness can sometimes \N be surprisingly near, can’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:21.30,Main,Juri,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:24.72,Main,Juri,0,0,0,,Anyway, this test \N is really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:26.63,Main,Juri,0,0,0,,Whose is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:31.18,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I looked over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:36.19,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,That teacher always gives \N tricky problems like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:38.41,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Try to keep that in mind \N for next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:42.31,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Must be nice, \N getting your test corrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:46.82,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Guess I need to get myself \N a logical boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:48.20,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Tenjou-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.03,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I’m Kaoru Miki. \N It’s a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.33,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,You know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:54.65,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:58.02,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,You’re the center of our \N attention as of late, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:07:59.04,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,“Our”?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.04,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Referring to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:03.83,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,You’re one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.21,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,You’re in the Student Council?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:09.09,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Then you must be \N after the Rose Bride, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.30,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,No! Please, \N don’t get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.60,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I may be a member of the Council,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:16.60,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,but I don’t want to duel \N to make Himemiya-san my bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.10,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:21.11,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Here are a few problems \N I expect will be on the make-up test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.10,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,If you just memorize \N the formulas in this notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.11,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,you should pass \N without any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.36,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:30.36,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:36.87,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like \N you’re awfully interested in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:44.35,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,She— Himemiya-san \N reminds me of a girl I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:47.97,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,That’s all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:52.04,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I don’t intend on challenging you \N to a duel, Tenjou-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.33,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Oh good, you’re not crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:58.31,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Do you guys in the Student Council \N know how much of a pain you’ve been to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:03.61,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,I don’t even know what’s going on, \N but we get roped into those stupid duels,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:06.73,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,and now thanks to that, \N we’re stuck studying for a make-up test.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:08.91,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,“We”?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.66,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,You’re retaking the test, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:16.54,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Um... Well... Yes.
Comment: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:16.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch}
Comment: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:33.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.58,Main,Touga,0,0,0,,It’s sounding very nice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:10:00.63,Main,Touga,0,0,0,,You’re not beating the piece into submission. \N Without that usual forcefulness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:02.58,Main,Touga,0,0,0,,...it sounds more graceful, \N somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:05.96,Main,Touga,0,0,0,,Could you have found that radiant thing \N you talked about once?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.55,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Yes. I might just have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:14.39,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I may finally be able to recapture \N something I lost long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.38,Main,Touga,0,0,0,,I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:51.45,Main,Touga,0,0,0,,If you do regain \N that radiant thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.88,Main,Touga,0,0,0,,...be sure to tell me \N what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.89,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,What is this \N “radiant thing”?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.20,Main,A-ko,0,0,0,,Have you heard? Have you heard? \N Oh, have you heard the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:09.94,Main,B-ko,0,0,0,,In elementary school, my first boyfriend \N was the best at math in the whole class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.13,Main,A-ko,0,0,0,,Oh? That’s news to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:13.20,Main,A-ko,0,0,0,,You had a boyfriend \N back then already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:16.49,Main,B-ko,0,0,0,,But... When he found out \N about my love of pro wrestling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:19.49,Main,B-ko,0,0,0,,...and super-sized bowls \N of garlic ramen, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.95,Main,A-ko,0,0,0,,“Now I know what kind of girl \N you truly are...”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:25.44,Main,B-ko,0,0,0,,...he said, and that was that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:27.27,Main,A-ko,0,0,0,,O Lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.46,Main,A-ko,0,0,0,,O Youth of Dreaming Love... {Oh, dreaming youth of love...}{夢見る恋の若人よ}{Edit if you don't like how little sense that makes but that's what she's saying}{Nah, if the Japanese doesn't make sense, the English doesn't have to either :D - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.25,Main,B-ko,0,0,0,,Of your girlfriend’s identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:33.50,Main,A-ko,0,0,0,,...have you heard the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:38.26,Main,Shadow Girls,0,0,0,,{\fad(0, 1750)}Have you heard? Have you heard? \N Oh, have you heard the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:41.51,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.85,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Sorry I’m late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:49.61,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Hey, we’ve been \N waiting for you. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:51.61,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:55.61,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Would you mind if I join?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.96,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Oh, you must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:11:59.22,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,I’m Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:00.37,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Miki-kun’s girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:02.12,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,A-Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:05.11,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Well, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:06.87,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Himemiya’s waiting inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:07.87,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Thank you for having us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.42,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Thank you for hosting us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:20.17,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:24.27,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,They say this dorm is like a haunted house, \N but it’s actually quite nice inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:25.77,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Such a lovely room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:29.77,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Yeah. That’s thanks to \N Himemiya’s daily cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:32.88,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,You enjoy keeping things neat, \N then, Himemiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.78,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Wow! I’m really impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:39.78,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Humph! Just you watch. Your days of thinking \N Himemiya Anthy is cute are soon to be over.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.78,0:12:43.90,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I envy you, Tenjou-senpai... \N getting to live with such a feminine girl.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.90,0:12:44.74,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Is that sarcasm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:47.75,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Himemiya-senpai? \N May I borrow an eraser?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.13,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,A snail! \N There’s a snail in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:57.86,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,She has a snail \N in her pencil case!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.57,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Himemiya! \N I’ve misjudged you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:01.64,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I’m so disillusioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:06.72,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,This is the end for you, \N Himemiya Anthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:09.46,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,That’s what’s going to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:14.44,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,I call it “Operation: Oh, My Gosh! Himemiya Anthy \N Is a Weirdo Who Keeps a Snail in Her Pencil Case!”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:16.47,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:17.44,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:20.22,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Then let’s begin with \N monomial expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.64,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:24.43,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,If you memorize the process, \N it’s like solving a puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:27.45,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Himemiya-senpai? \N May I borrow an eraser?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:29.91,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Himemiya Anthy...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.32,0:13:32.42,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:46.04,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,S-S-S-S-S-S-S-S-Snails! \N There’s s-snails in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:49.72,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,Oh, that’s my snail friends’ home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:52.49,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,I always tell her \N not to keep them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.13,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,But it’s so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:56.30,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,It’s very much like \N Himemiya-san to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:59.06,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,They’re s-snails! \N What’s cute about s-snails?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:02.33,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,I’ll see you later, \N Catherine, Juliet, Marcelina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:08.04,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I see the issue, Tenjou-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:09.56,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Here’s where you \N made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:10.81,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Oh, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:11.65,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,In this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:14.63,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Well, then, \N you leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:19.83,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,My, what a pretty desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.59,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,I wish I had one like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.35,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,A garter snake! \N There’s a garter snake in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:32.02,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,She has a garter snake \N in her desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:33.74,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Himemiya! \N I’ve misjudged you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:35.85,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I’m so disillusioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:40.86,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,At last! This is the end for you, \N Himemiya Anthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:43.55,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,That’s what’s going to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:49.58,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,I call it “Operation: Oh, My Gosh! Himemiya Anthy \N Is a Weirdo Who Has a Garter Snake in Her Desk.”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.64,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:52.58,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:58.59,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,For triangle ACP, line BX \N is parallel to line CP, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:01.28,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,My, what a pretty desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.09,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,I wish I had one like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:14.76,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,My garter snake...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:18.86,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,The snake I spent all night catching...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:22.65,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,Oh, that’s Mr. Mongoose’s home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.51,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,I said not to keep him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:27.11,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,But it’s so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:29.12,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,It’s very much like \N Himemiya-san to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.34,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,It’s a mongoose! \N A mongoose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.24,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Don’t you think that’s weird?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:36.30,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,We’re studying now, \N so I’ll have to see you later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.84,0:15:38.88,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,Did Mr. Snake taste yummy? \N How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:43.21,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Hmm... So what do I do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.21,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Ah, you do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.88,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.04,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.80,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,If that’s how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.79,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,I didn’t want to do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:54.41,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,but you leave me no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:03.36,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,A live octopus! \N There’s a live octopus in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:08.33,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,She keeps a live octopus \N in her closet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:10.10,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Himemiya! \N I’ve misjudged you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.87,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I’m so disillusioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:17.66,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,This really is the end for you, \N Himemiya Anthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:21.60,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,That’s what’s {\i1}guaranteed{\i0} to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:27.13,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,I call it “Operation: Himemiya Anthy Is a Total \N Weirdo Who Keeps a Live Octopus in Her Closet!”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:29.21,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.89,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:38.35,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,This time for sure, \N with this live octopus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.90,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,...I’ll have you begging for mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.86,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Himemiya Anthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.52,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,You’ll be {\i1}crying{\i0} for mercy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:46.53,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,...because of this real, \N living octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.58,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:01.33,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Live octopus! Live octopus! \N Live octopus! Live octopus! Live octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.92,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,It’s dangerous to just go \N and open that closet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:05.61,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,This can’t be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.71,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,This has to be a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.86,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,This massive live octopus...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.53,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,And its octopus tentacles...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:15.72,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Isn’t that the inflatable they used \N for last year’s school festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:20.45,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,I felt so sorry about it \N getting thrown away that I hid it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:23.44,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Won’t you please talk her into \N getting rid of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:25.23,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,But it’s so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.54,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,It’s very much like \N Himemiya-san to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:35.56,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,So, now x equals three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:39.35,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,And if you substitute it here, \N you can solve this linear equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:42.58,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Oh, now I see! \N Three plus y is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.29,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:46.48,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,And so... Got it! \N How’s this look?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:50.97,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:52.06,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Now I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:54.84,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,You don’t disappoint, Mr. Genius! \N That was way easier than class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.28,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Oh, hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:03.75,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Let’s take this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.98,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,The test is next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:08.16,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,Yes, Utena-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.39,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Wow, it’s already this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.06,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Hey, Miki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:17.85,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:19.60,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Wanna get a bite to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:20.50,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,And you, Nanami-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:25.62,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Nanami-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.66,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Um... Oh, yes. Supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:32.27,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Actually, I packed \N a little something for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:34.51,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,I hope you all enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.90,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Another animal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:43.98,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,I suppose this is another one of \N Himemiya-senpai’s friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:46.35,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,Chu-Chu! You can’t just...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.59,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,These animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:55.40,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,I’m sorry! I’ll go make \N something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.56,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,Lemon and strawberry \N taste nice together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:02.25,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.81,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,She’s right! This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:06.61,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,This is my special recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:08.98,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,You don’t say! \N I should write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.21,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Can I get a little more \N syrup on mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:15.08,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,Nanami-san, you should have some \N before it melts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.93,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,You’ve got to be kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:19.81,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,You should be more polite \N to an upperclassman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:22.92,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Snails in her pencil case... \N A mongoose in her desk...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:26.03,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,A giant octopus balloon \N in her closet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.67,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,And to top it all off, \N shaved ice for supper?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:31.99,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,I’ll get a stomach ache!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.52,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,I have a very delicate stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.39,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I, for one, like shaved ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:38.49,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Don’t blame her \N for your weak stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.48,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,This isn’t about the ice \N or my stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:45.50,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Why are you two \N so interested in her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:49.99,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Didn’t you say you wanted to be \N Himemiya-san’s friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:51.50,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,What’s that you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.70,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,You’re the one \N who likes her, Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.03,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,Confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:56.21,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:59.01,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Huh? Himemiya’s gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.59,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,You’re right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:03.97,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Maybe I shouldn’t have pushed her \N to be in a study group.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.99,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,Maybe takoyaki would have been \N a better choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.99,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,I’m gonna go look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:19.99,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I’ll come with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:26.58,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,A piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:30.64,Main,Nanami,0,0,0,,That’s the song you always play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:21:00.86,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Wow. I didn’t know \N she could play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:10.21,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,She plays with the same \N timbre as my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:12.66,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,That sunlit garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:27.67,Main,Miki,0,0,0,,I’ve found it... \N My radiant thing!
Comment: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:41.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:56.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.36,0:23:01.90,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Himemiya! You have to \N play the piano for Mickey!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.90,0:23:05.14,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,He seems really fixated \N on your playing.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.14,0:23:07.13,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,If you insist, Utena-sama.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.13,0:23:08.82,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,No, don’t do it because I say so.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.82,0:23:09.95,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Do it for Mickey’s sake.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.95,0:23:11.29,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,I am the Rose Bride.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.29,0:23:13.75,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,I will do whatever \N my fiancé requests.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.75,0:23:19.25,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Wake up, Mickey! This isn’t the way \N to get Himemiya to play for you!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.25,0:23:20.88,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,Next time, \N on Revolutionary Girl Utena:
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.88,0:23:22.61,Main,Utena,0,0,0,,“The Sunlit Garden - Finale”
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.61,0:23:24.90,Main,Anthy,0,0,0,,The absolute destiny: apocalypse.
